  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4463277">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4463277/" class="title-link">没落与崛起</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4463277"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lixiaowensailor/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4534723-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lixiaowensailor/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">李柏衣</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-11-14"
      class="main-meta">2010-11-14 10:49:08</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4463277_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《1914-1945年的海上战争》是这套书的最后一本，也是离我们这个时代最近的海上大规模战争。虽然没有前两本精辟的分析，虽然没有具体的战例研究，但是其对各个战役的背景的叙述还是值得一读的。 从两次世界大战的海战中我们可以看出，新崛起的海军强国和没落中的海洋大国之间的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4463277_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4463277_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





